# Loaded for `vite` / `vite dev`. Overrides: `.env.development.local` (gitignored).
# Path `/v1` = same origin as the Vite dev server; `vite.config.ts` proxies to the backend on 8080.
# If you bypass the proxy and call nginx/backend directly from the browser, use an absolute URL instead, e.g.:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/v1
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/v1
